The paper deals with image transformations and machine learning techniques, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) is a key aspect of the proposed method, which is also a popular topic in deep learning (cs.DL) sub-category. The problem of removing staff-lines in music score images involves image processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
